description: Your next home could be this luxurious move-in ready 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom unit at 637 East 1st Street!  The kitchen features white shaker cabinets, high end stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and a comfortable island. The kitchen is open to a large open concept living/dining space that easily accommodates a large table for dining, great for entertaining. The living area offers plenty of seating, a gas fireplace and opens up to one of two private decks with a gas line.  The spacious primary bedroom fits a king sized bed, offers room for a sitting area, has a large walk-in closet, direct access to the 2nd private deck and an en-suite bathroom with double vanity and walk in shower.  There is a generous guest room along with guest bath with tub. Deeded garage parking, in-unit laundry, private storage, 10 foot ceilings, hardwood floors and central air complete this terrific offering. Close to Seaport, East Broadway and all that South Boston has to offer. Come see for yourself!
